<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-q-and-a-living-kidney-donation-may-be-option-for-those-with-type-2-diabetes/">Mayo Clinic Q and A: Living kidney donation may be option for those with type 2 diabetes</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
